{"tid":2283240,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"刀劍點解會成為神作","createTime":"2020-11-12T11:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T12:59:36.000Z","uid":231600,"like":5,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c837f795d6b3ec6ad20e066445e67010ffa2a970","tid":2283240,"uid":231600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"因為刀劍係運用咗中國古代陰陽嘅力學<br />\n陰=阿斯娜<br />\n陽=桐人<br />\n陰陽人=結衣<br />\n一套動畫入面竟然可以套用陰陽力學真係少之有少，而且仲可以伸延到陰同陽嘅結合，將生命溶入呢種代表世界性嘅文化入面。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有睇過空之境界，應該會知道主角兩儀式係一個陰陽人，有雙重性格，但點解佢唔可以成為神作，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"green\">因為佢冇解釋到何謂陰陽，只係將佢炒埋一碟。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然佢最後尾係有生左個女，但係佢係抄刀劍舊橋，所以根本毫無新意，狗也不屌。<br />\n<br />\n刀劍就行反傳統，即刻係身處虛擬世界，但係只要有愛，你就可以突破極限，得到「陰陽」嘅資格。<br />\n<br />\n所以刀劍先係神作。"},{"pid":"6608263e4c722bbefc9e1469fb6b8f6d0dad1d9c","tid":2283240,"uid":63124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:56:40.000Z","msg":"0/10<br />\n冇是咁的"},{"pid":"419cdccf17897320e025b237422fc904295a6e80","tid":2283240,"uid":310656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c26a50e079c17fa9ab442323a1c2fac27892f1","tid":2283240,"uid":25494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:18:21.000Z","msg":"入來&gt;負評&gt;上一頁"},{"pid":"2b38b77cd5521049b25269306c43f30d82b85406","tid":2283240,"uid":112551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:20:37.000Z","msg":"死毒撚日日夜夜都諗動畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fa1d09dba8c316651e36055fbe489c9293b94d","tid":2283240,"uid":222771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:21:42.000Z","msg":"比你老母見到你咁好咩?"},{"pid":"5f96817b2d480c077b144e7a4e30f5de89442b4a","tid":2283240,"uid":299548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:27:08.000Z","msg":"撐刀劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ybiEdD3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FybiEdD3.png&h=4061de7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"404b48e9255c78dd9cd11d93466755962707fdcd","tid":2283240,"uid":22949,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"鬼滅先至係神作好無"},{"pid":"32490aaa50a6b8a5e2f894d7cd9fa2965a2b5135","tid":2283240,"uid":231600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"404b48e9255c78dd9cd11d93466755962707fdcd","tid":2283240,"uid":22949,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"鬼滅先至係神作好無"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:38:31.000Z","msg":"鬼滅的確係好睇<br />\n但差咁啲情懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f9530c3216dc3590a36f29b0a675bf5a936215","tid":2283240,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:41:41.000Z","msg":"因有公廁娜"},{"pid":"4c1a1b886985640b1bffc30c8e471e86b32ab481","tid":2283240,"uid":300690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:48:20.000Z","msg":"因為佢唔係"},{"pid":"86ff5410ec2a82ff2212b590a6095646c9288201","tid":2283240,"uid":10422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:49:46.000Z","msg":"同鬼滅比 刀劍的確係神作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf12bd7a9a496a9b3308874b15b43d75e459796","tid":2283240,"uid":81308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:59:36.000Z","msg":"多左啦 收返埋啦"}]}